{"tid":1539360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831太子站個位15歲小朋友以家點呀","createTime":"2019-09-04T09:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:59:08.000Z","uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"191a7d28e44f36968775e40996a3f2cc1d8b8325","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"好似話送左去瑪嘉烈<br />\n有冇人Fact check 到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90bcf07b7d203ada3bfa3077aed8a8b3a2d6c6d","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d15c8dfde87660f57092fa8d17f74231dbcce556","tid":1539360,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:45:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">大個仔</span>獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 大核彈<span style=\"font-size: small;\">內容包括</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">：</span></span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7758120cb871f30b17b5561e689b8465b047a6e8","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:47:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07abb724b0af9f7350e60bf0b7bcb251ecf413f9","tid":1539360,"uid":228437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:47:49.000Z","msg":"903太子係謀殺！一圖就明邊個打邊個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539239</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n尋日太子站15歲果個，根本消失左，唔好俾黑警轉移視線"},{"pid":"cc3ea6d6bf79c9d1619fb98fdb98ad8c12df6268","tid":1539360,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:48:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"328ce5f1a58665447c80cad14b3bc234cd240a09","tid":1539360,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"191a7d28e44f36968775e40996a3f2cc1d8b8325","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"好似話送左去瑪嘉烈<br />\n有冇人Fact check 到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"就係唔知"},{"pid":"3a3b91ada5e98ba7f8d429225d26f4a62755c260","tid":1539360,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"191a7d28e44f36968775e40996a3f2cc1d8b8325","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"好似話送左去瑪嘉烈<br />\n有冇人Fact check 到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},