21a1d646","tid":1539360,"uid":268725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:00:05.000Z","msg":"點會一直都冇消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8B39Niu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8B39Niu.png&h=c9eeccd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8067bf984be2821056efdad7c65452f72cc6b58","tid":1539360,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"【831太子恐襲】今日下午約3時，兩位親身經歷8.31太子站警察無差別襲擊事件的目擊者，於立法會議員毛孟靜陪同下召開記者會，講述事發經過及其經歷。<br />\n目擊者講出多樣警方及醫管局未有提及的消息 ，目擊者指，831傷者被送往瑪嘉烈醫院而非廣華，而早前729曾爆出有瑪嘉烈醫院醫生於Facebook稱「大大力打」，更有留言稱「唔夠架生通知聲」 、「盡情打」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民即時整合重點如下：<br />\n- 有一人失蹤<br />\n- 有機會有一人 已經死亡<br />\n   - 被警察毆打近半個鐘至嘔白泡<br />\n   - 警員見他沒有反應，方停止毆打<br />\n   - 二三十分鐘後由消防員（非救護員）送走，\u0003而該傷者完全無反應<br />\n- 警員對他們說「強姦佢地係正常」<br />\n- 有被捕人士 於警署被非禮 (摸胸)<br />\n- 於警署如廁時不能關門，同時有異性警員在場<br />\n-  有日本人被捕 ，警方拒絕讓他聯繫大使館<br />\n- 目擊者稱傷者被送去 瑪嘉烈醫院，而非廣華醫院<br />\n- 速龍落電梯時，是 用腳踩市民背部甚至頭部<br />\n<br />\n#立場新聞 直播全片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2383919765184466/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F2383919765184466%2F&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcatDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=53a9889c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2383919765184466/</a><br />\n#831太子 #太子恐襲 #毛孟靜 #立法會 <br />\n-<br />\n發聲社新聞 STP Media<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stpmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstpmedia&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcatDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=7b4a328c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stpmedia</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.singthepress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singthepress.com&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcatDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=01b1eb4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.singthepress.com</a>"},{"pid":"5449d9c34666c7ba771a6142f6323735db3f2789","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n林鄭廢話可以唔睇<br />\n要搞清以件事先"},{"pid":"c6ea72075a8cfb413eaaf543ecaafd0bdfbc295c","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c2e4f16e65fe21df16e3f20a7ff74e00c1aac9","tid":1539360,"uid":91041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:58:33.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗去瑪嘉烈睇下咩情況<br />\n有無醫護fc ???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"希望有醫護巴絲收到風"},{"pid":"e216c59d2a28220a38cb401c5ca8d88a461ee01a","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ac436d20d2560487821fe0903cf9b67a032dc074","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:06:45.000Z","msg":"根據今日講法<br />\n小朋友比人打左半個鐘嘔白泡<br />\n之後搵消防(極大機會藍絲)做急救唔揾救護<br />\n好大機會出事呀"},{"pid":"52bf18872c3953592b11a6142209cb1e60762e5e","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:07:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"789b7fb03fa35c4b2e37639ffcd50fe1f8b601c1","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:07:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ba82be37088ae0cd9bb1079cb000f7d596e3fd88","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:08:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f3a737894c6eba00cc2e896e7bc87d081d235a97","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fa2e7f665a6d9e8e89bc23e049f2c061ab49736f","tid":1539360,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:09:21.0